T1  - Linear Program-Based Approximation for Personalized Reserve Prices
AU  - Derakhshan, Mahsa
AU  - Golrezaei, Negin
AU  - Paes Leme, Renato
Y1  - 2021/04/05
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2022/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3897
