T1  - Hospital Financial Health and Clinical Choices: Evidence from the Financial Crisis
AU  - Adelino, Manuel
AU  - Lewellen, Katharina
AU  - McCartney, W. Ben
Y1  - 2021/10/04
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2022/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3944
